{{2025 Atlantic Coast Conference football standings}}

The '''2025 Atlantic Coast Conference football season''', part of the [[2025 NCAA Division I FBS football season]], was the 73rd season of [[college football]] play for the [[Atlantic Coast Conference]] (ACC). The entire schedule was released on January 27, 2025.<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|date=January 27, 2025|title=ACC Reveals 2025 Football Schedule|url=https://theacc.com/news/2025/1/28/acc-reveals-2025-football-schedule.aspx|access-date=June 11, 2025|website=theacc.com|language=en}}</ref>

The [[2024 SMU Mustangs football team|SMU Mustangs]] were the defending regular season champions and the [[2024 Clemson Tigers football team|Clemson Tigers]] were the defending champions.

