=== ACC Kickoff ===
The 2025 ACC Kickoff was held from July 22 through 24 at the Hilton Charlotte Uptown in [[Charlotte, North Carolina]]. Coverage of the three day event was televised by the [[ACC Network]]. The event was reduced from four days to three days in 2025.<ref>{{Cite web |date=February 27, 2025|title=2025 ACC Football Kickoff Set for July 22–24 in Charlotte|url=https://theacc.com/news/2025/2/27/2025-acc-football-kickoff-set-for-july-22-24-in-charlotte.aspx|access-date=June 11, 2025|website=theacc.com|language=en}}</ref>

